These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different games are played: billiard, bridge, domino, whist
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, coral, emerald, purple
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, snowmobile, subway, van
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
4. the person playing billiard is the person who likes pink##1
5. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
7. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Game    | bridge  | whist | domino    | billiard       |
| Color         | coral | purple    | emerald      | pink |
| Transport   | bike   | subway | snowmobile | van        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different games are played: billiard, chess, canasta, poker
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, turtle, cat
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
2. the person playing poker is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the bike is the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Game        | canasta   | chess | billiard     | poker      |
| Pet         | horse | turtle | cat | hedgehog |
| Transport   | car    | roller   | motorbike     | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rat, mouse, bird
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, hip-hop, pop
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, water, coffee
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the bird is the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking water##1
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | rat | mouse | bird |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | electronic    | country | hip-hop     |
| Beverage   | cola | water    | coffee | hot-chocolate    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, firefighter, freelancer, project-manager
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, mirinda, almond-milk, tea
4 different pets are kept: pony, horse, lizard, goat
1. the freelancer is the owner of the goat##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the firefighter is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the freelancer##1
7. the freelancer is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
8. the project-manager is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | architect | project-manager | freelancer | firefighter |
| Beverage       | mirinda     | tea      | sprite     | almond-milk      |
| Pet   | horse | pony         | goat      | lizard        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, canasta, snooker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, horror, thriller, western
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, december, april, february
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the person playing scrabble is the person watching horror movies##1
7. the person playing snooker is the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Game         | canasta   | snooker | backgammon  | scrabble      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | epic        | western  | horror       |
| Birthday         | november | april    | december | february |

