.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
City: san-francisco, venice, rome, berlin
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, dutch, nigerian, turkish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, reggae, trance
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of trance##1
3. the colombian is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to venice is on the far left##1
6. the nigerian is the person traveling to rome##1
7. the fan of funk is on the right of the dutch##1
8. the person traveling to berlin is the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| City           | venice | rome | berlin | san-francisco |
| Nationality   | turkish   | nigerian  | dutch | colombian   |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | folk     | reggae | funk       |

