.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, scooter, trike, ship
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, iced-tea, juice
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, spy, thriller
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is the person driving the trike##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person drinking cola is the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Transport          | snowmobile  | ship | trike   | scooter     |
| Beverage         | juice | cola   | sprite  | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre   | spy         | disaster  | mystery | thriller  |

