.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, tram, helicopter, skateboard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, crime, drama, mystery
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, blues, gospel, dubstep
1. the person driving the tram is the fan of gospel##1
2. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
6. the fan of dubstep is the person driving the helicopter##1
7. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
8. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Transport      | skateboard | helicopter     | motorbike | tram |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | animation | drama       | crime    |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | dubstep | hip-hop    | gospel |

