.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, onion, pepper, tomato
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, woodworking, traveling, baking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, horror, adventure, sports
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is the person eating onion##1
5. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
7. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | pepper        | tomato   | onion  | cucumber   |
| Hobby   | dancing         | baking     | woodworking    | traveling       |
| Movie-Genre         | horror | fantasy | adventure | sports |

