.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
House: modern, townhouse, tower, ranch-style
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, spinach, tomato, zucchini
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, designer, engineer, freelancer
1. the ranch-style house is the freelancer##1
2. the designer is on the left of the engineer##1
3. the tower house is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
4. the modern house is on the right of the freelancer##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
6. the tower house is on the left of the freelancer##1
7. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| House   | townhouse    | tower | ranch-style | modern        |
| Food       | zucchini | pumpkin  | spinach | tomato     |
| Job        | designer    | engineer   | freelancer  | project-manager |

