.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, hip-hop, disco, dubstep
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, volleyball, weightlifting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, epic, adventure, horror
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is the person watching adventure movies##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Music-Genre         | r&b  | dubstep | hip-hop  | disco |
| Sport       | volleyball | rugby        | weightlifting | cricket       |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy   | epic          | horror          | adventure       |

