.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, cooking, dancing, traveling
4 different pets are kept: horse, goldfish, mouse, snake
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, soul, metal, indie
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the snake is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of house##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is the fan of metal##1
7. the fan of indie is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling   | dancing   | card-games | cooking |
| Pet   | mouse | horse | goldfish   | snake |
| Music-Genre   | indie     | house  | metal  | soul  |

