1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the thai is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the thai##1
4. the thai is on the left of the spanish##1
5. the indian is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the thai is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the indian is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling | chess    | baking        | reading |
| Beverage   | iced-tea     | juice     | tea        | almond-milk   |
| Nationality         | russian   | indian | thai | spanish  |

