.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, drama, mystery, superhero
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, skiing, soccer, rowing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, prince, baccarat, montecristo
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
4. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama   | superhero  | comedy    | mystery    |
| Sport   | rowing | soccer  | weightlifting  | skiing |
| Cigar     | montecristo  | prince | baccarat | dannemann        |

