.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, video-games, hiking, puzzles
City: venice, san-francisco, colone, paris
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, handball, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is climbing is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person traveling to paris is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person who's hobby is writing is the person traveling to venice##1
8. the person traveling to colone is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Hobby      | writing        | puzzles    | video-games | hiking      |
| City   | venice        | paris   | san-francisco  | colone  |
| Sport         | weightlifting | handball | soccer   | climbing |

