The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, fantasy, superhero, thriller
House: farmhouse, modern, ranch-style, wooden
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
2. the wooden house is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the right of the modern house##1
4. the person who growstulip is the ranch-style house##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growslily##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the person who growslily##1
7. the person who growslily is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Flower          | iris     | bellflower   | lily | tulip |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | thriller | superhero | fantasy   |
| House           | wooden    | modern     | farmhouse      | ranch-style     |

