.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-17::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, bartender, lawyer, scientist
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, dunhill, montecristo, alhambra
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, lemon, apple, blueberry
1. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person eating apple##1
2. the bartender is the dunhill-smoker##1
3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
4. the montecristo-smoker is the person eating lemon##1
5. the lawyer is on the far left##1
6. the scientist is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
7. the person eating apple is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Job           | lawyer  | architect | bartender  | scientist |
| Cigar   | montecristo    | tiparillo       | dunhill | alhambra      |
| Food   | lemon | pumpkin  | blueberry    | apple    |

