.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, february, april, december
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, nigerian, pakistani, russian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, spy, western, epic
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
4. the pakistani is on the far right##1
5. the indonesian is the person watching western movies##1
6. the russian is on the far left##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
8. the russian is on the left of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Birthday           | february  | april  | august | december |
| Nationality   | russian   | indonesian | nigerian   | pakistani      |
| Movie-Genre         | mystery | western    | spy   | epic         |

 